{"tid":405943,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[比人放上連登]希望各位巴打幫下我","createTime":"2017-09-19T08:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T15:17:21.000Z","uid":148421,"like":55,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc12d92bdf78eba51f4d4519bf30080a5297c6d9","tid":405943,"uid":148421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/400773/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/400773/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n相信好多人都應該有睇到依個post<br />\n無錯，樓主影個個的確係我<br />\n當我上個星期睇到個陣我仲好嬲唔知點算<br />\n因為我都著左幾年都係咁，未試過比人放上網<br />\n好彩我以前都有上開舊登上到黎連登<br />\n到知道左個陣已經對樓主有d頭緒<br />\n因為影個個位置係學校既6樓，6樓係電子科<br />\n雖然唔同班，但對一對樓主個名都有d印象<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為樓主個名有個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">牛</span>字</span><br />\n而讀電子科既人有一個人個名有牛字!!!<br />\n最後終於比我搵到佢出黎，但我又唔夠膽當面鬧佢<br />\n因為佢有好多朋友，而且應該係回應個到出現過一齊推post<br />\n我只好上黎搵各位巴打幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家幫幫我"},{"pid":"9e11797c7385980a94ee42845ebaa3cf8082e1bb","tid":405943,"uid":25112,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚廢上嚟求人幫你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自貼一張先啦"},{"pid":"7bcfec6c62a370a72c91052a006b0ba50922bd5e","tid":405943,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T08:56:05.000Z","msg":"我都見過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08775964af6fe0973c13d33846c60ad553a31cab","tid":405943,"uid":148421,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/165603_79dddc56c292f43dd003ecaae5373db5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F165603_79dddc56c292f43dd003ecaae5373db5.jpg&h=0bd0698c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖